query:
SELECT ff.id, ff.execucaoFormandoId, ff.cenarioId, ff.numeroArquivos, ff.observacao, ff.createdAt, tc.nome as cenario
FROM fotos_formando ff
LEFT JOIN tipos_cenario tc ON ff.cenarioId = tc.id
ORDER BY ff.id DESC
LIMIT 10
